snippet.textDisplay:
I was single when this song got released back in 2015 & I loved it at first hearing! 
Now I have a 3 years old daughter & each time I listen to this song I get deeply emotional (actually I cry) thinking that one day she will leave her birth place and start new journey at new home leaving us behind. Earlier I loved the music but now I realize the lyrics.
